trading.title: Hokohoko

portfolio.title: Kōpaki
portfolio.description: He rōpū whakahaere kōpaki whānui mō te aroturuki i ngā rawa, te tātari i te whakatutukitanga, me te whakahaere i ō taputapu pūtea puta noa i ngā papaaho katoa.

wallet.title: Whakahaere Pūkoro

transactions.title: Hītori Whakawhitinga

transfers.title: Whakawhitinga

investments.title: Haumi

plans.title: Mahere Haumi

ico.title: Hokonga Tohu

marketplace.title: Maakete

nft.title: Whare Puoro NFT

store.title: Toa
store.description: Maakete hirahira e whakaatu ana i ngā hua matihiko me te tinana me te tukatuka utu haumaru, te tuku ao whānui, me te tiaki kaihoko.

services.title: Ratonga

affiliate.title: Kaupapa Hoa

support.title: Pokapū Tautoko

faq.title: Puna Mōhiotanga
faq.description: Tuhinga whānui, akoranga, me ngā pātai auau hei āwhina i a koe ki te whakanui i ngā āheinga papaaho.

insights.title: Tirohanga
